      "rationale": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical) used with validated version control and regression test suite. FDA in-house solver subject to agency SQA procedures. Required level 2 achieved through documented version tracking and benchmark suite execution."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Patch test and single-element benchmark problems executed for all element types used. Linear elastic patch test passed to machine precision. Code verification documented in solver qualification report."
    },
    {
