      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study conducted with three mesh densities (coarse, medium, fine). Richardson extrapolation applied; discretization error in peak von Mises stress estimated at less than 2.1%. Fine mesh selected for production runs."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
