      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by independent analyst not involved in primary model development. Boundary condition application, material assignment, and contact pair definitions independently verified against simulation plan document."
