      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic isotropic material law adopted for titanium alloy implant and UHMWPE blocks; justified by strain levels remaining below 0.2% in all components. Contact modeled with penalty-based frictionless formulation consistent with lubricated test fixture interface."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
