      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions mapped directly to test fixture geometry and actuator displacement control protocol. Fixture compliance characterized experimentally and incorporated into model. Input parameter equivalency table documented with traceability to test records."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
