      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using ASME V&V 20 area validation metric. FEA construct stiffness predictions fall within experimental 95% confidence interval for 10 of 11 specimens. Mean absolute relative error 4.7%; maximum 9.2%. Statistical equivalence test (TOST) passed at alpha=0.05."
    },
